I would like to have question about "TaskCompleted" in Events

TaskCompleted - Raise this event when task is completed (indicates success/failure). Here is how an example of the event section.
 `
{
       "TaskStarted":
       {
          "Timeout": "00:05:00"
       },
       "TaskCompleted":
       {
          "Timeout": "00:07:00"
       }
